{"lemma":"حَفْلِ","slug":"حَفْلِ","root":"ح.ف.ل","root_slug":"ح-ف-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/ح-ف-ل","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":3,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":15},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n8512","n8516","n8517"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AD%D9%8E%D9%81%D9%92%D9%84%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to gather, to assemble (intransitive)"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to rain violently"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to flow in abundance"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to collect (transitive)"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to smooth, to polish"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be afraid"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to give care and attention"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to gather, to assemble (transitive)"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to adorn, to decorate"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of حَفَلَ (ḥafala) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of حَفَلَ (ḥafala) (form I); gathering, assembling"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"crowd, large assembly"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"performance, show"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"celebration, festival"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"heed, attention"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n8512","headword_ar":"حَفَلَ","root":"Hfl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HafolN","text_ar":"حَفْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HufuwlN","text_ar":"حُفُولٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HafiylN","text_ar":"حَفِيلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", said of water, and of milk (K) in the udder (TA) [or breast],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It collected;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tHif~l","text_ar":"تحِفّل","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AHtfl","text_ar":"احتفل","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K, TA. [In the CK,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AHatafalahu","text_ar":"احَتَفَلَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is erroneously put for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AHotafala","text_ar":"احْتَفَلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HafolN","text_ar":"حَفْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"collecting of water,"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"its becoming collected, in its"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maHofil","text_ar":"مَحْفِل"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning its"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"place of collecting."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hafala Ald~amoEu","text_ar":"حَفَلَ الدَّمْعُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HafolN","text_ar":"حَفْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The tears became copious."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K, TA.) In some copies of the K,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nvr","text_ar":"نثر"},{"kind":"text","text":"is here erroneously put for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kavura","text_ar":"كَثُرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hafala AlwaAdiY","text_ar":"حَفَلَ الوَادِى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biAls~ayoli","text_ar":"بِالسَّيْلِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The valley brought the torrent so as that it filled its sides;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AHtfl","text_ar":"احتفل","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) or the latter signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the valley became filled by the torrent:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AHtfl AlwAdY","text_ar":"احتفل الوادى"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the valley became full, and flowed."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hafalati Als~amaA='u","text_ar":"حَفَلَتِ السَّمَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HafolN","text_ar":"حَفْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The sky rained vehemently:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the rain fell profusely."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, * M, TA.) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hafalato","text_ar":"حَفَلَتْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", said of a woman,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"She collected the milk in her breasts."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And of camels, one says, (K in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$kr","text_ar":"شكر"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hafalato mina Alr~abiyEi","text_ar":"حَفَلَتْ مِنَ الرَّبِيعِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They abounded in milk,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"had their udders full, from the herbage called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rbyE","text_ar":"ربيع"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S and K in that art. [See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaAfilN","text_ar":"حَافِلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]) ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hafala Alqawomu","text_ar":"حَفَلَ القَوْمُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HafolN","text_ar":"حَفْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Msb;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AHtflwA","text_ar":"احتفلوا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, Msb, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The people,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"party, collected themselves together"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K) in a sitting-place: (Msb:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"they collected themselves together, aiding one another,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for one thing"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"affair;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AHt$dwA","text_ar":"احتشدوا"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HafaluwA lahu","text_ar":"حَفَلُوا لَهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They combined for him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"on his account,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and took pains,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"exerted themselves, in treating him with courtesy and honour;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ha$aduwA lahu","text_ar":"حَشَدُوا لَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Fr, L in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"H$d","text_ar":"حشد"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b7-  See also 8.       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hafalahu","text_ar":"حَفَلَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see 2.       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hafalotu bifulaAnK","text_ar":"حَفَلْتُ بِفُلَانٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I managed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"conducted, the affair,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"affairs, of such a one."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biAlA^umuwri","text_ar":"بِالاُمُورِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AHtfl","text_ar":"احتفل","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He managed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"conducted, affairs,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the affairs, well."},{"kind":"text","text":"(IDrd, K.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hafalotu ka*aA","text_ar":"حَفَلْتُ كَذَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I cared for, minded, heeded,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"regarded, such a thing."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA Hafalahu","text_ar":"مَا حَفَلَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA Hafala bihi","text_ar":"مَا حَفَلَ بِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HafolN","text_ar":"حَفْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bihi","text_ar":"بِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mA AHtfl","text_ar":"ما احتفل","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lahu","text_ar":"لَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; so in the T and TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rbA^","text_ar":"ربا"},{"kind":"text","text":"];"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He did not care for, mind, heed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"regard, it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA taHofilo bihi","text_ar":"لَا تَحْفِلْ بِهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Do not thou care for, mind,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA","text_ar":"لَا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taHofilo biA^amorhi","text_ar":"تَحْفِلْ بِاَمْرهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Do not thou ask his affair, nor be disquieted thereby."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.)       -A4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hafalahu","text_ar":"حَفَلَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HafolN","text_ar":"حَفْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it, made it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rendered it, clear, unobscured, apparent, plainly apparent,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"conspicuous;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA;) as, for instance, black hair the colour of a pearl, increasing [in appearance] its whiteness; (TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"exposed it to view; displayed it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jalaAhu","text_ar":"جَلَاهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[perhaps here signifying also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he polished it"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["K","TA","M","S","Msb"]},{"entry_id":"n8516","headword_ar":"حَفْلٌ","root":"Hfl","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A company"},{"kind":"text","text":"of men; as in the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Einodahu HafolN mina Aln~aAsi","text_ar":"عِنْدَهُ حَفْلٌ مِنَ النَّاسِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"With him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"at his abode, is a company of men"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: originally an inf. n. (S.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamoEN HafolN","text_ar":"جَمْعٌ حَفْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HafiylN","text_ar":"حَفِيلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[which latter is also originally an inf. n. (see 1 and 8)]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A numerous company."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*uwHafolK","text_ar":"ذُوحَفْلٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*w HafolapK","text_ar":"ذو حَفْلَةٍ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HafiylN","text_ar":"حَفِيلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY A^amorihi","text_ar":"فِى اَمْرِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) A man"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"who exerts himself,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his power"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"efforts"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"endeavours"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ability,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"who takes pains"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"extraordinary pains, in that which he sets about."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, TA.) And ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axa*a liloA^amori Hafolatahu","text_ar":"اَخَذَ لِلْاَمْرِ حَفْلَتَهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He strove,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"laboured; exerted himself,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his power"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"efforts"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"endeavours"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ability;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"took pains"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"extraordinary pains; in the affair."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Sgh, K.)"}],"source_refs":["K","S","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n8517","headword_ar":"حِفْلٌ","root":"Hfl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HufaAlapN","text_ar":"حُفَالَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}